videos.description: Kellan Grady and Davion Mintz pull and knock down back-to-back 3-pointers to extend the Wildcats' lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Grady and Mintz drill back-to-back 3's for Kentucky

videos.description: Clear the runway as Jacob Toppin flies in for the big-time block at the rim for Kentucky.
videos.headline: Jacob Toppin elevates for the filthy rejection for Kentucky

videos.description: Scotty Pippen Jr. crosses his defender and drills the and-1 from beyond the arc for Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Scotty Pippen Jr. buries the and-1 from 3-point land

videos.description: Tyrin Lawrence drives and somehow gets the and-1 to fall for the Commodores.
videos.headline: Tyrin Lawrence with the sweet and-1 bucket for Vanderbilt

videos.description: Jordan Wright is "cooler than the other side of the pillow" as he drills the step-back jumper to take the lead.
videos.headline: Wright with the smooth step-back basket for Vanderbilt

videos.description: Jordan Wright and Rodney Chatman drill back-to-back 3-pointers to take the lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Wright and Chatman bury back-to-back 3's for Vanderbilt

videos.description: It's showtime in Tampa as Oscar Tshiebwe elevates for the block on one end of the court and TyTy Washington Jr. drills the 3-pointer on the other.
videos.headline: Kentucky gets it done on both ends of the court

videos.description: Jacob Toppin gathers the dish from Oscar Tshiebwe and drains the jumper to seal the victory for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Toppin pulls up and drills the jumper to seal the victory for Kentucky

videos.description: Following a quarterfinal victory over Vanderbilt, Kentucky's Oscar Tshiebwe stresses the importance of playing team ball in order to win.
videos.headline: UK's Tshiebwe: 'It's not about me, it's about the team'
